          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-c36f0b02d2b6bcb2",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Review all other product rates\nMortgage rates\nLoans and lines of credit rates\nPersonal bank account rates\nBusiness bank account rates\nGIC rates\nCIBC Business GIC Rates\nTFSA rates\nRRSP rates\nRRIF and LIF rates\nMutual fund rates\nExchange Traded Fund (ETF) Rates of Return\nFHSA rates\nGIC interest rates shown below are prevailing rates. Prevailing rates are also referred to as posted rates.\nRates are calculated on an annual basis and are for the annual interest and at-maturity interest payment options. Rates may change anytime without prior notice. For GICs with different interest payment options, call us at 1-866-525-8622 Opens your phone app. .\nOpens your phone app.\nRates as of RDS%SYSTEM_DATE(#M# #d#, #Y#)%\nRDS%SYSTEM_DATE(#M# #d#, #Y#)%",
